"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:11.2.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">11.2.2</span> 标题：弥那（mina）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מָנֶה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：maneh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:17\">1KI 10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:70\">NEH 7:70</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:71\">NEH 7:71</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:12\">EZK 45:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">兰：מְנֵא</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mne’)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:25\">DAN 5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:25\">DAN 5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:26\">DAN 5:26</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：μνᾶ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mna)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:13\">LUK 19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:16\">LUK 19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:16\">LUK 19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:18\">LUK 19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:18\">LUK 19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:20\">LUK 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:24\">LUK 19:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:24\">LUK 19:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:25\">LUK 19:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc14:24\">1MA 14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc15:18\">1MA 15:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc1:4\">3MA 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:44\">1ES 5:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:44\">1ES 5:44</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>上述词语是指“弥那”。大多数学术权威认为<em>maneh</em> （弥那）等于50舍客勒，1他连得等于60弥那。然而，有些权威认为1弥那为60舍客勒，1他连得等于50弥那（参<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:12\">EZK 45:12</a> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:17\">1KI 10:17</a> ：这节经文记载，金盾牌的重量为“三弥那”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）。大多数通俗译本将其换算为现代单位，例如“接近四磅”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）、“接近两千克”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:69</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:70\">NEH 7:70</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:71\">NEH 7:71</a> （《和》7:71–72）：翻译者通常用弥那来表示这里的<em>maneh</em> 所指数量（带或不带注），或者采用现代的换算值。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:69</a> 中短语的字面意为“五千弥那银子”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> ）的译法有些沉重，作“两千七百五十千克银子”。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 把数值圆整到与原文数值的有效位数相同，英文意为“约六千磅银子”。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:12\">EZK 45:12</a> 把1弥那定义为60舍客勒。这在圣经中是不同寻常的，可能代表一个较高的“皇家”数值。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:13\">LUK 19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:16\">LUK 19:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:16\">LUK 19:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:18\">LUK 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:18\">LUK 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:20\">LUK 19:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:24\">LUK 19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:24\">LUK 19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:25\">LUK 19:25</a> ：在这个比喻中，仆人所得的东西几乎肯定是一笔钱，而不是某个重量的东西。这笔钱的确切价值不是重点，重点是三个仆人用他们领受的东西做了什么。翻译者应该记住，一<em>mna</em> （弥那）大约是一个工人四个月的工资。虽然确切的数额不重要，但他们领受的数额相同却是有意义的。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 对于<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:13\">LUK 19:13</a> 第二个分句的译法没有明确表明这一点，英文意为“给他们每个人一些钱”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 类似）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> 的译法值得借鉴，意大利文意为：“给他们每个人相同数额的钱。”<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 把<em>mna</em> 译为“a coin”（“一枚钱币”），这可能会误导读者，因为现今没有任何国家流通有如此高额的钱币。该译本的脚注特别指明了这是一大笔钱，约为三个月的工资，但这是不准确的。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 的“a gold coin”（“一枚金币”）仅仅略好一点。最好译成“一大笔钱”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>对于<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:25\">DAN 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:25\">DAN 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:26\">DAN 5:26</a> 中的亚兰文<em>mne’</em> （弥那），参上文<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">11.1.4 毗勒斯、乌法珥新（peres, parsin）&lt;REALIA:11.1.4&gt;</a> 关于毗勒斯的讨论。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
